<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #1e40af;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #1e40af;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Admission Offer</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div style="padding: 20px;">
            <p>Dear {{applicantName}},</p>
            
            <p>Congratulations! We are delighted to inform you that you have been offered admission into the <strong>{{programme}}</strong> programme for the <strong>{{session}}</strong> academic session.</p>
            
            <h3>Offer Conditions:</h3>
            <p>{{{offerConditions}}}</p>
            
            <p><strong>Reporting Date:</strong> {{reportingDate}}</p>
            
            <p>To accept this offer and proceed with registration, please log in to the student portal using the button below:</p>
            
            <a href="{{portalUrl}}" class="button">Login to Portal</a>
            
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact the Admissions Office.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            COELS Admissions Team</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 COELS. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
